71 action against donors to student scholarship organizations if the commissioner
72 preapproved a donation for a tax credit prior to the date the student scholarship
73 organization is removed from the Department of Education list pursuant to Code
74 Section 20-2A-7, and all such donations shall remain as preapproved tax credits subject
